{
	"events": [
		{
			"event_id": "dialogic_024",
			"set_theme": "theme-1727627785.cfg"
		},
		{
			"background": "res://Dialogue/Picture/cvhapter2/valDoor1.png",
			"event_id": "dialogic_021"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d1.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "Valen stands before a massive, sealed door with five glowing locks. The door hums with a strange magic, blocking his path. He examines it, trying to figure out how to pass through."
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d2.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1721952703.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "This door… it's not a normal one. It feels like it's tied to some kind of sequence, maybe something repeating. "
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d3.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1721952703.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "There’s no key, no handle. How do I get through?"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d4.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1721952703.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "Gandalf once said, “in the world of C# magic, loops help us repeat actions until a condition is met. Different loops for different situations.”"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d5.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1721952703.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "I remember… he taught me about while, do-while, and for loops."
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d6.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "(The locks on the door shimmer as if responding to his thoughts.)"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d7.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1728009045.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "“With a while loop, Val, you check a condition first. If it’s true, you keep going. It’s great when you don’t know how many times you need to repeat something.”"
		},
		{
			"background": "res://Dialogue/Picture/cvhapter2/unit2s1/valDoor1tutorial.png",
			"event_id": "dialogic_021"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d8.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1721952703.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "Maybe I need to unlock each part while the door is still sealed. I could imagine it like this:"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d9.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1721952703.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "I’d keep going while there are locks still in place. The condition is that I stop when all five are unlocked."
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Music and Sounds/sound effects/unlock.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "..."
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d10.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "One of the locks clicks open slightly, as if responding to his thoughts."
		},
		{
			"background": "res://Dialogue/Picture/cvhapter2/valDoor1.png",
			"event_id": "dialogic_021"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d11.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1728009045.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "The do-while loop... is a little different. It always executes at least once before checking the condition, making sure you perform the action at least once."
		},
		{
			"background": "res://Dialogue/Picture/cvhapter2/unit2s1/do while.png",
			"event_id": "dialogic_021"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d12.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1721952703.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "What if I need to try something first before checking the door’s state? Something like:"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d13.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1721952703.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "I’d get at least one lock open before I even check."
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Music and Sounds/sound effects/unlock.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "..."
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d14.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "(Another lock clicks open, the magical barriers weakening slightly.)"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d15.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1728009045.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "“And the for loop, is when you know exactly how many times you need to repeat something. You set the condition right from the start.”"
		},
		{
			"background": "res://Dialogue/Picture/cvhapter2/unit2s1/forloop.png",
			"event_id": "dialogic_021"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d16.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1721952703.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "If I know there are exactly five locks, a for loop might be the most efficient here. Like this:"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d17.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1721952703.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "Straightforward, just like Gandalf taught. I’ll unlock all the locks, one after another, until it’s done."
		},
		{
			"background": "res://Dialogue/Picture/cvhapter2/valDoor2.png",
			"event_id": "dialogic_021"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d18.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "Valen reaches forward, and using his knowledge, he runs his hand across the door. One by one, the locks click open in a sequence. The door shudders and finally opens."
		},
		{
			"background": "res://Dialogue/Picture/cvhapter2/valDoor3.png",
			"event_id": "dialogic_021"
		},
		{
			"audio": "play",
			"audio_bus": "Master",
			"event_id": "dialogic_030",
			"event_name": "AudioEvent",
			"file": "res://Dialogue/Voice/NEW/timetravel/level2/stage1/c2l2stage1p1/c2l2stage1p1d19.wav",
			"volume": 0
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1721952703.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "I did it. Just like Gandalf said—different loops for different situations. The while loop checks first, the do-while always tries once,\nand the for loop is perfect when you know exactly how many steps you need."
		},
		{
			"character": "",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "Badge Received!"
		},
